        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Historic Tax Credit Enhancement Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to eliminate the requirement for a taxpayer to reduce the basis of a building by the amount of the tax credit determined for the rehabilitation of a certified historic structure. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
